root.name: Daa! Daa! Daa! Totsuzen Card de Battle de Uranai!?
root.description: OverviewDaa! Daa! Daa! Totsuzen Card de Battle de Uranai!? is a game developed and published by Video System for the Game Boy Color. Daa! Daa! Daa! Totsuzen Card de Battle de Uranai!? was never released outside of Japan.
